parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The warping and failure of brake rotors can cause the vehicle to vibrate or pull to one side when braking, leading to reduced stopping power and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Warped or grooved brake rotors
pulsation or vibration when braking
squealing or grinding noises when braking
uneven brake pad wear
and reduced stopping power.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Anti-Lock Brake System (ABS) and Skid Control System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS and Skid Control System can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Illumination of ABS and Skid Control System warning lights
sudden loss of traction
vehicle skidding or sliding
and difficulty stopping or controlling the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to seize or become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel seizes without warning
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the steering column is not securely connected
the emergency brake lever fails to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of a crash, leading to increased risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag pops out without a crash
the airbag does not deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fraudulent sales practices of dealerships can lead to financial losses for consumers and compromise their safety on the road.
symptoms: The dealership fails to disclose known defects
the dealership resets the odometer or warning lights
the dealership refuses to take back the vehicle or provide a refund.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Wear of Steering and Suspension Components
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature wear of steering and suspension components can cause loss of control and potential accidents.

the vehicle makes noise while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corroded connection can cause the vehicle to stall, potentially leading to accidents or fires.
